Class SSLSocks5

  • java.lang.Object
    • fucksocks.client.Socks5
      • fucksocks.client.SSLSocks5
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    SocksProxy

    public class SSLSocks5
extends Socks5
    The class SSLSocks5 represents a SSL based SOCKS5 proxy. It will create a SSL based connection between the client and SOCKS5 server.

        public SocksProxy copy()
        Description copied from interface: SocksProxy
        This method can create a same SocksProxy instance.
